<h1 class="header">Let's go somewhere.</h1>
<h1>Where are we starting?</h1>

<%= form_tag('/pages/search') %>
  <%= text_field_tag 'query' %><br />
  <%= radio_button_tag(:list, 'cities', checked: true) %>
  <%= label_tag(:list, 'Major Cities') %><br />
  <%= radio_button_tag(:list, 'parks') %>
  <%= label_tag(:list, 'National Parks') %><br />
  <%= submit_tag "Let's Go" %>
<br />You give a city or address, and we'll find out how far it is to some big cities or national parks.
